1.1.0 SNAPSHOT
==============
- Fixed issue with scanned date not being properly updated when running the link scanner (December 30, 2008)
- Fixed issue with user-defined checkboxes being unchecked when user edited links or accounts (February 3, 2009)
- Fixed issue with account signup date not being set properly (March 4, 2009)
- Updated reciprocal link detection to better handle large blocks of HTML code (March 11, 2009)
- Fixed issue with last backup date not displaying properly (April 1, 2009)
- Fixed error message generated when last link of an import file does not contain a valid category (June 3, 2009)
- Fixed issue with quick tasks and add link icons not working in the Search Links interface (July 29, 2009)
- Removed requirement of Zend Optimizer (March 22, 2010)
- Removed requirement of OpenSSL extension (March 22, 2010)
- Software now provided completely as source with no encoded files (March 22, 2010)
- Removed dsbl.org blacklist checking since that service is now offline (April 12, 2010)
- Fixed issue with # of categories per page not working properly in the Manage Categories interface (April 12, 2010)
- Improved support for PHP 5.3 (April 15, 2010)

